96,000 for a 60-minute 'webcam show'.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CamSoda\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CamSoda\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CamSoda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CamSoda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That sum dwarfs the \\u00a339,400 handed out by World Athletics to athletes who win a gold medal in France.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999903602657, \"rank\": 9.639700540177154e-09, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9359147628997423, \"rank\": 0.06846161295180618, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vice president of the company, Daryn Parker, said: \\\"If it was up to me, I'd award you for what everyone else saw, your talent below the belt.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1040, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aloysius_Parker\", \"score\": 0.9999999971505531, \"rank\": 2.8305917123383964e-09, \"text\": \"Parker\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aloysius_Parker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aloysius_Parker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"s a lover of crotch-centric activities, I'd love to offer you up to $250,000 in exchange for a 60-minute webcam show, in which you show off your goods, minus the crossbar, of course.\\\"\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.21733413851544e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999930127213159, \"rank\": 6.987327545901902e-06, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ammirati, a former under-20 world champion, is yet to comment publicly on the offer.\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And immediately after the games, he appeared to avoid talking about the finer details of his final failure, claiming it was a lack of competitive action that eventually cost him.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a bit gutted, because I did not miss anything on the third attempt at 5.70m.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What I did miss was a bit of jumping in training to fine-tune the settings.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just a tech